menu_buildjob_stockpile
[TITLE]The Manual: Stockpile Menu[/TITLE]
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]How to Get Here[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Press [IKEY:D_BUILDJOB] from the main view and move to a stockpile.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Description[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Here you can customize stockpile settings.
[B]
You can make one pile want items from another pile.
Once you select "take from a pile", move to another pile and press [IKEY:SELECT].
You'll see the second pile appear in a list.
[B]
